videos.description: Christian Turner's long touchdown is called back due to him stepping out of bounds while running down the sideline.
videos.headline: Long Michigan TD called back

videos.description: Feleipe Franks finds Van Jefferson for a 41-yard pass that leads to a Gators field goal for the first points of the game.
videos.headline: 41-yard pass leads to first points of game

videos.description: Donovan Peoples-Jones catches a fade pass from Shea Patterson to get Michigan on the board in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Peoples-Jones gets Michigan on the board

videos.description: J'Marick Woods blocks Tommy Townsend's punt to set Michigan up at Florida's 30-yard line in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Michigan blocks Florida punt

videos.description: Feleipe Franks keeps the ball as he runs 20 yards for a go-ahead Florida touchdown in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Franks keeps ball for Gators TD

videos.description: Feleipe Franks puts up 100 passing yards and 70 rushing yards along with a touchdown as Florida leads Michigan 13-10 at halftime of the Chick Fil-A Peach Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Florida pulls ahead of Michigan before half) 2018/12/29 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Florida pulls ahead of Michigan before half

videos.description: Chauncey Gardner-Johnson fools Shea Patterson pre-snap and picks him off before a 53-yard return into Michigan territory.
videos.headline: Gardner-Johnson picks off Michigan's deep shot

videos.description: Feleipe Franks finds Lamical Perine wide open off a screen as Florida extends its lead over Michigan to 20-10 in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Franks finds Perine for walk-in TD

videos.description: Feleipe Franks pitches the ball to a wide-open Jordan Scarlett who waltzes in for a short touchdown.
videos.headline: Franks pitches to Scarlett for Gators TD

videos.description: Michigan's touchdown is reversed in the fourth quarter after the replay reveals that Tarik Black does not maintain possession in the end zone.
videos.headline: Michigan TD overturned in fourth

videos.description: Lamical Perine breaks free for 53 yards on third-and-20 for a Gators touchdown that all but secures their Chick-Fil A Peach Bowl win.
videos.headline: Perine punctuates Florida domination with long TD

videos.description: Michigan blocks a punt that rolls out of the end zone for a safety in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Michigan blocks punt for safety

videos.description: No. 10 Florida dominates No. 7 Michigan behind Feleipe Franks' 259 yards of total offense as the Gators win the Chick-fil A Peach Bowl 41-15.
